});

nexusCore.start();
nexusCore.load();
nexusCore.shutdown();
nexusCore.destroy();

Some key enhancements in the code include

* Lifecycle observer pattern implemented
* Encapsulation of NexusCore instance configuration
* Status management with INIT and SHUTDOWN states
* Method chaining for `configure`, `load`, and `shutdown`
* Robust handling of lifecycle events using the `observe` method.